            "short": "Pak Khlong Talat is Bangkok's 24-hour wholesale flower market—a riot of colors, smells, and activity where florists buy orchids, roses, marigolds, and lotus flowers by the truckload. Located near the Old City by the river, it's most atmospheric late at night or very early morning when deliveries arrive and vendors prepare bouquets. It's working commerce, not a tourist attraction.",
